===Etymology===
Via {{F.}} "personal property" from {{L.}} ''[[capitale]]'' "of the head". Compare ''[[capital]]''.
=== Noun ===
'''cattle''' (plural)
# four-legged [[ruminant]] [[mammal]]s of the bovine genus. Male: [[bull]] (uncastrated), [[steer]] (castrated).  Female: [[cow]]. Young: [[calf]]. Young male: [[bullock]]. Young female: [[heifer]].
#: ''Do you want to raise cattle?''
# certain other domestic animals, such as [[sheep]], [[pig]]s or [[horse]]s
# (''Rare.'') [[beef]].
#: ''I hate eating cattle.''

